<br>
The dark figure slipped past the guards, then up the stairs, and into Kyimera's room.  From her mantle, the figure took a well worn mandolin; a worthless relic to most.  Whispered words were spoken to the sleeping figure.<br>
<br>
&quot;I am sorry, dearest... but I need this again.&quot;<br>
<br>
The figure departed, the melody disappeared, people awakening as if nothing had happened. <p>Felitus<br>
